Fig. : Some of the radial fiber bundles are myelinated (Fig. 7d).
Fig. : Only an occasional fiber extends beyond the inner spiral bundle into the area of the outer hair cells (Fig. 7d).
Fig. : Even at this late stage in maturation there are still numerous spiral neurons present in the apex (Fig. 7c,7d).
